Mark Zuckerberg my inspirational person







        I learn many things about the key of success from Mark, that I have many ways to get all my dreams come true.                     



        "Simplified
your life." Maybe the clause can motivate my life to be better. When I
am doing something, I will try to maximum my potential. With positive
thinking I am sure that God will help me to do my work.

        Many ways to get success, especially
 from Mark I get one key of success. First at all, I should pay
attention for the things that I like it. Second, we must do it earlier than
others. Next, it is important to be a successful person, I have to be focus in
one goal that I make.             

      After Mark succeeded, he gives pledge for other who need help and  he gives attention for many
people arround him. It inspires me to be a successful person, and I
will do the same like Mark do. I can be an impact for people arround me. 


            





